Sync PullNew Push
Expunge Slave
Create Slave

MaildirStore s_l
Path ~/.mail/s/
Inbox ~/.mail/s/

ImapStore s_r
Host imap.gmail.com
UseIMAPS yes
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
User s@fomichev.me
Pass PASSWORD

Channel s_inbox
Master :s_r:[Gmail]/Входящие
Slave :s_l:inbox

Channel s_archive
Master :s_r:[Gmail]/Вся\ почта
Slave :s_l:archive

Channel s_mephi
Master :s_r:[Gmail]/mephi
Slave :s_l:mephi

Channel s_saved
Master :s_r:[Gmail]/saved
Slave :s_l:saved

MaildirStore kernel_l
Path ~/.mail/kernel/
#Inbox ~/.mail/kernel/

ImapStore kernel_r
Host imap.gmail.com
UseIMAPS yes
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
User kernel@fomichev.me
Pass PASSWORD

Channel kernel
Master :kernel_r:
Slave :kernel_l:


Group kernel
Channels kernel

Group all
Channels s_inbox s_archive s_mephi s_saved kernel
